ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  "sparql_query": "PREFIX ss: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX ex: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/data/lbnl-example-2#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone WHERE {\\n  # every Zone instance\\n  ?zone a ss:Zone .\\n  \\n  {\\n    # ---- Directly associated property -----------------------------------\\n    ?zone ss:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  }\\n  UNION\\n  {\\n    # ---- Indirect connection via a RoomDomainSpace ----------------------\\n    # walk from the zone to a RoomDomainSpace through any number of\\n    # typical building‑model relationships\\n    ?zone (ss:hasDomainSpace|ss:contains|ss:encloses|ss:hasConnectionPoint|ss:isConnectionPointOf|ss:connected|ss:connectedTo|ss:connectedFrom|ss:connectedThrough|ss:connectsTo|ss:connectsFrom|ss:connectsAt|ss:connectsThrough|ss:hasPhysicalLocation|ss:hasAspect|ss:hasMedium|ss:hasValue|ss:hasExternalReference|ss:hasRole|ss:mapsTo|ss:observes|ss:hasObservationLocation|ss:hasDomain)* ?rds .\\n    ?rds a ex:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    # from that RoomDomainSpace walk to a property (any property class)\\n    ?rds (ss:hasProperty|ss:hasConnectionPoint|ss:isConnectionPointOf|ss:connected|ss:connectedTo|ss:connectedFrom|ss:connectedThrough|ss:connectsTo|ss:connectsFrom|ss:connectsAt|ss:connectsThrough|ss:contains|ss:encloses|ss:hasPhysicalLocation|ss:hasAspect|ss:hasMedium|ss:hasValue|ss:hasExternalReference|ss:hasRole|ss:mapsTo|ss:observes|ss:hasObservationLocation|ss:hasDomain|ss:hasDomainSpace)* ?prop .\\n    # make sure ?prop is really a Property (its type ends with \\"Property\\")\\n    FILTER EXISTS {\\n      ?prop a ?ptype .\\n      FILTER (regex(str(?ptype), \\"Property$\\", \\"i\\"))\\n    }\\n  }\\n}\\n"\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 37, 16, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
